description:
Blood Bowl 3 Season 6 smashes in with not one, but TWO new factions! Brace yourselves for the madcap mischief of the Goblins and the scrappy resilience of the Halflings! Don’t underestimate these pint-sized players, they’re ready to brawl! The pitch just got a lot more dangerous... and a lot more hilarious!
